Fair Housing? FAIR...at least to us...(the people) is OFF-THE-TABLE!
Laws aren't kept...or applied!
What a mess we have created housing ourselves in this City of Angels...
Hopeless Homeless fill our dirty, overgrown streets!
Landlords rule!
For years the Courts are filled with "Judges" who have a huge "Conflict of Interest"...(they own property, they are LANDLORDS!)...laws aren't applied...things back-up!
We didn't keep up with need... greed kept AFFORDABLE HOUSING a joke in this City.
There is no ACCOUNTABILITY
no one standing up...and  stopping this mess!
Instead of "STREAM-LINING" and organizing..."they", (who's in charge here?) create another Agency...hire more people and compound the problem.
They aren't "FUSING" resources so the right-hand-doesn't-know-what-the-left-one-is-doing!
That sets up confusion...(who is really suppost to do what?)...a "Big-Time-Pass-the-Buck-System" occurs...we, the people get caught in!
It's BROKEN...(actually fractured in several places). It needs to be UNITED!
Seems NO Agency takes care of Harrassing Landlords that Cheat...big time!
No "teeth" in the law means we, the People, have no Governance that works for us...no "REAL TIME PROTECTION."
The end result...look around the dirty, overgrown, weed-infested, broken side-walks, "narley" pot-hole infested streets of Los Angeles...record holder of "the largest Homeless Population in the Country."
(What ever happened to "Operation Sparkle," our City-wide clean-up?)
Employ a "night crew" to do proper, full inspections. Da!
My eyes are on a case where the "Landlord" moved "illegally housed" tenants belongings... stove...frig...bed...everything out...(to hide them from Inspectors). They're now sleeping on the floor (of a converted garage)...for weeks....they are so desperate. It's that or the street...(you can't even sleep in your car legally any more!)
The Tenant reporting got his car keyed...threatened with an electric drill...reported to the Police (as a "trouble maker"), denied parking and was made a "target " of harassment!
I know there are "laws on-the-books" to PROTECT us...but they are totally useless if we can't ever APPLY them.
He was told:
1) I can't see them...
2) We don't have ANY NIGHT TIME Inspectors
3) We take "harassment complaints" at another Division
4) Go to Police...file a Complaint...another Division
5) I suggest you file with Building and Safety...another Division
6) I suggest you file a complaint with The Health Department...another Division
By the time a person has to run this many places (paid parking $10.00) and try to work...put up with the Landlord hassle...take care of fragile family needs (that are caused by the fear)...repair a damaged car...try to look for a non-existent place to move out of this "Hell"...there is NO HELP FORTHCOMING FROM ANY AGENCY. They all "passed-the-buck" to each other...with a scolding..."They shouldn't have told you that...they are always sending us people...we don't do that...I'm going to report this to my Supervisor...you have to go here...maybe there...I'm not sure who handles that...you have to call...here's a Brochure...or
the ever-present wonder-pass...GO ON LINE!" They might as well tell you..."that goes right in the dead file...no action required!"
Someone needs to step in and clean this mess out...we are way too "backed-up." We can't go on too much longer like this...we have already reached CRITICAL MASS and it's still growing folks.
(I think it's time The Mayor steps in! Don't you?)
People are Living in unsafe conditions while our government employees are "ride'n easy"...taking a "good" pay check home.
When you're enjoying "yours"...think about how many have no home...and if there was anything more you could have done?
(Remember...your pay comes out of our pockets!)
My wish for the new Year:
Dig a little deeper...see what you (as a human being caught up in this mess) can do to...STAND-IN-PLACE-AND- HELP! Extend yourself!
We are all in this together. Help each other! Whenever and wherever we can!
"PEACE on Earth...GOOD WILL toward man..."</Text>

< Review>
I absolutely love this place. The staff here is just the best. They are kind, caring, and informative. Dr. Alsop (I probably spelled it wrong) is just really great. He is honest and straight forward. He knows what to do and isn't afraid to get in there and do it. I always leave with a smile on my face. He has really helped my quality of life. With regular visits my back hasnt gone out once yet since I have been with him. Where as before I had a lot of pain often and would spend week's at a time in bed. I even used to get shots in my back every 6 months to help. I no longer need any of that. Though chiropractic care isnt for everyone I highly recommend it with Dr. Alsop. We addressed my concerns and knew I was uncomfortable with the idea of someone messing with my back and was kind and thoughtful.
Thank you to the entire staff at this location you are all amazing and caring.</Review>

I have Orkin inspect the outside of my house and front and back yards every 3 months for maintenance. The make full inspection and brush under the roofing for any spiders or anything else that might be there.
